version_description:
· Stay updated on all your matches.
· Get notifications on 'Daily recommendations', 'Who viewed your profile', 'New matching profiles' and 'Who shortlisted me'.
· Now you can upload upto 10 pictures in your account.
· Editing your profile is now easy and you can add more details in one go.
· Scroll and communicate with other members better.
· Overall user-experience has been improved.
